translated: Årholm, Hedvigr Elise, dentist, Varberg, b. 17/4/05 in Arbrå, Gävle County. 1st marriage, married in 1931 to dentist Simon Årholm. — Completed high school in Uppsala in 1924, dental studies 1929, became a dentist in 1930. Assistant at dental institute, department of dental fillings, in 1930, worked as an assistant there until 1931. Started practicing dentistry in Varberg since 1932. Became the chairperson of Varbergs women's shooting association since its establishment in 1939, chairperson of the Halland women's shooting federation. Received the State's Master marksmanship award in rifle shooting and national medal in 1940. Participated in pistol shooting, became a champion of the Halland shooting federation.
